C:\Program Files\Java

open google

type jdk 8 download

goto http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html site

accept license agreement 

select jdk with respect to OS and bit size

click on download

paste that download in personal folder

double click on that download

click run

click next until finish

goto Control Panel\System and Security\System\advanced system setting

environment variables

system variables

select path and click edit 

add path of jdk\bin;

close properties

